WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.240
Hey, good morning everybody. I just wanted

00:00:02.040 --> 00:00:05.100
to come on here and tell you some more

00:00:03.240 --> 00:00:07.980
things the Lord has showed me in prayer

00:00:05.100 --> 00:00:09.660
time.

00:00:07.980 --> 00:00:10.920
I'll tell you some positive

00:00:09.660 --> 00:00:12.719
things, some good

00:00:10.920 --> 00:00:15.420
things, but I have to tell you this first,

00:00:12.719 --> 00:00:17.880
and this is not so good.

00:00:15.420 --> 00:00:19.619
I want to be uplifting.

00:00:17.880 --> 00:00:21.840
I don't want to stir up fear or make

00:00:19.619 --> 00:00:24.060
anybody afraid, but

00:00:21.840 --> 00:00:26.759
I have to tell you what the Holy

00:00:24.060 --> 00:00:29.698
Spirit is telling me. There are things that we

00:00:26.760 --> 00:00:31.800
can avoid and some things I

00:00:29.699 --> 00:00:33.899
don't think we can.

00:00:31.800 --> 00:00:37.680
I feel I'm a watchman,

00:00:33.899 --> 00:00:41.399
like I've said, and it's my job to

00:00:37.680 --> 00:00:45.000
tell you what's going on. There was

00:00:41.399 --> 00:00:47.340
a massive barge traveling down

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:50.100
the Mississippi River. I could see rust

00:00:47.340 --> 00:00:52.020
on the side of this barge; it was like a

00:00:50.100 --> 00:00:54.300
big boat. It was supposedly

00:00:52.020 --> 00:00:55.980
carrying grain or something out of the

00:00:54.300 --> 00:00:58.680
north somewhere. There was black

00:00:55.980 --> 00:01:01.500
all around the top of it. The area

00:00:58.680 --> 00:01:03.180
where the captain or

00:01:01.500 --> 00:01:04.799
the person who drives the boat sits

00:01:03.180 --> 00:01:06.659
was white and had rust on it. It

00:01:04.799 --> 00:01:09.240
looked like it was weathered. There was

00:01:06.659 --> 00:01:12.060
a little

00:01:09.240 --> 00:01:15.539
square opening on

00:01:12.060 --> 00:01:17.159
the deck part. They

00:01:15.540 --> 00:01:19.200
were moving,

00:01:17.159 --> 00:01:22.439
went out into the Gulf of Mexico,

00:01:19.200 --> 00:01:23.880
and turned their boat to

00:01:22.439 --> 00:01:26.580
face

00:01:23.880 --> 00:01:30.420
east. They opened the hatch

00:01:26.580 --> 00:01:32.820
and put out a rocket. They

00:01:30.420 --> 00:01:35.579
lifted it

00:01:32.820 --> 00:01:37.979
up. The men on

00:01:35.579 --> 00:01:40.559
this boat were

00:01:37.979 --> 00:01:43.979
Asian;

00:01:40.560 --> 00:01:46.380
I have no idea if it was

00:01:43.979 --> 00:01:49.200
China or whatever, but

00:01:46.380 --> 00:01:53.220
they raised this rocket up. It was

00:01:49.200 --> 00:01:54.899
about five feet tall and

00:01:54.899 --> 00:02:00.060
probably about a

00:01:57.960 --> 00:02:04.139
foot to two feet thick at the most.

00:02:00.060 --> 00:02:07.920
It was black and white and

00:02:04.140 --> 00:02:11.580
had USSR written on the

00:02:07.920 --> 00:02:15.300
rocket. They shot the rocket out over

00:02:11.580 --> 00:02:17.879
America, and when they did, it exploded.

00:02:15.300 --> 00:02:20.040
But I kept hearing in the spirit

00:02:17.879 --> 00:02:22.500
realm, 'It's not going to get high

00:02:20.040 --> 00:02:24.780
enough.'That's

00:02:22.500 --> 00:02:27.780
what I was hearing.

00:02:24.780 --> 00:02:32.520
It went out over the Tennessee and

00:02:27.780 --> 00:02:35.459
Kentucky area, Atlanta,

00:02:32.520 --> 00:02:37.800
Mississippi, Alabama, and then

00:02:35.459 --> 00:02:41.940
it went up

00:02:37.800 --> 00:02:44.400
by Ohio and exploded right over all

00:02:41.940 --> 00:02:47.760
that area. When it did, it was an

00:02:44.400 --> 00:02:49.560
EMP, and the EMP turned out all the lights.

00:02:47.760 --> 00:02:53.160
Because it didn't get high

00:02:49.560 --> 00:02:55.500
enough, it didn't have a blast

00:02:53.160 --> 00:02:57.840
radius that affected everything

00:02:55.500 --> 00:03:00.540
way over

00:02:57.840 --> 00:03:04.140
to the west, but it affected all of

00:03:00.540 --> 00:03:06.540
Virginia and Pennsylvania.

00:03:04.140 --> 00:03:10.200
It was terrible; complete

00:03:06.540 --> 00:03:13.079
darkness was over this area. The further west

00:03:10.200 --> 00:03:16.440
you went, it wasn't as dark, and things

00:03:13.080 --> 00:03:20.280
weren't affected as badly. I could see

00:03:16.440 --> 00:03:24.359
that people in places like Colorado did not have

00:03:24.360 --> 00:03:29.340
cell phones,

00:03:26.640 --> 00:03:34.079
internet, or

00:03:29.340 --> 00:03:37.680
cable TV.

00:03:34.080 --> 00:03:40.019
They had TVs with bunny ears

00:03:37.680 --> 00:03:42.720
and landline telephones, and

00:03:40.019 --> 00:03:44.340
they still had electricity. You weren't

00:03:42.720 --> 00:03:46.140
able to have a whole

00:03:44.340 --> 00:03:48.299
bunch of stuff going; the power grid was really

00:03:46.140 --> 00:03:51.779
weak, but you were still able to

00:03:48.299 --> 00:03:54.120
power things. I

00:03:51.780 --> 00:03:55.739
don't understand it all; I just see

00:03:54.120 --> 00:03:57.360
things whenever I'm praying.

00:03:57.360 --> 00:04:02.640
I could see the emergency broadcast

00:03:59.700 --> 00:04:04.560
come on. I could hear it, and they were

00:04:02.640 --> 00:04:06.599
warning the people of what happened. You

00:04:04.560 --> 00:04:08.400
know how they warn you with the

00:04:06.599 --> 00:04:11.159
emergency broadcast alerts

00:04:08.400 --> 00:04:12.780
on our TVs?

00:04:12.780 --> 00:04:18.418
They ran that because it

00:04:15.540 --> 00:04:21.599
turned the TV on, and you could hear

00:04:18.418 --> 00:04:24.120
the emergency broadcast going off.

00:04:21.600 --> 00:04:27.180
I had some friends call the

00:04:24.120 --> 00:04:30.300
landline at my house, and they asked, 'Do you have power?'I said,

00:04:27.180 --> 00:04:31.979
'Yes.'I

00:04:30.300 --> 00:04:33.360
went to my

00:04:31.979 --> 00:04:35.039
refrigerator, opened it up,

00:04:33.360 --> 00:04:38.639
and there was still a light

00:04:35.040 --> 00:04:42.780
on inside.

00:04:38.639 --> 00:04:46.380
Looking out south, I could see

00:04:42.780 --> 00:04:48.239
in the spirit realm

00:04:46.380 --> 00:04:51.120
that

00:04:48.240 --> 00:04:53.639
the sycamore trees had leaves on

00:04:51.120 --> 00:04:55.979
them. It was still really warm outside.

00:04:53.639 --> 00:04:57.300
Whenever I'm seeing in the

00:04:55.979 --> 00:04:59.639
spirit and the Lord is showing me something,

00:04:57.300 --> 00:05:02.639
I always try to pay attention to

00:04:59.639 --> 00:05:05.940
my surroundings: the trees,

00:05:02.639 --> 00:05:08.040
the weather, and the warmth

00:05:05.940 --> 00:05:10.020
outside, how it feels, you know, how I

00:05:08.040 --> 00:05:12.120
would have assumed it to feel, where the

00:05:10.020 --> 00:05:13.198
sun is at, everything. I try to pay

00:05:12.120 --> 00:05:15.540
attention because you can always tell

00:05:13.199 --> 00:05:18.300
where we are in the season. The sun was setting more towards the southwest, so it was a summer

00:05:28.500 --> 00:05:34.500
month, probably late summer.

00:05:31.199 --> 00:05:37.080
So, this was basically

00:05:34.500 --> 00:05:40.199
the end of it, but it was a warning of

00:05:37.080 --> 00:05:44.039
an EMP attack upon our nation. I

00:05:40.199 --> 00:05:46.500
know it's a heavy message,

00:05:44.039 --> 00:05:48.120
but I want to tell you about things

00:05:46.500 --> 00:05:52.080
that the Lord shows me to pray about.

00:05:48.120 --> 00:05:54.060
It's not to stir up fear; I believe we

00:05:52.080 --> 00:05:56.460
can stop things through intercessory

00:05:54.060 --> 00:05:59.699
prayer. I tell people this stuff

00:05:56.460 --> 00:06:01.440
to warn you to pray.

00:05:59.699 --> 00:06:03.539
Thank you so much for

00:06:01.440 --> 00:06:05.940
watching this video. Hopefully, it didn't

00:06:03.539 --> 00:06:08.180
freak you out too bad. Have a blessed day,

00:06:05.940 --> 00:06:08.180
everybody.

